list.name: Default
list.comment: Made a single nuvi filereader function a reader for all nuvi files; made a ui for user to choose a type of file to process; updated NuviDailySummary to include "trendType" to differentiat the items it reads in; also updated nuvi reader to read up to 10 lines of text. Commented out monogo stuff.

task.summary: Added "printWeeklyGrosses()" function to attempt to access data from our "weeklyGrosses" collection in our mongodb.
Set up new class ClientTicketGross in preparation for sending over objects to front end; also fixed up TicketGross data (removed startDate attribute); and then added more dummy data.
Created a new class SproutDailySummary for storing our Sprout data. Created file GetSproutData to read in Sprout CSV files.
Added Apache POI Excel File reader libraries; added started code for reading an excel file; code must still be modified further to process file properly for each line.
Adding Apache libraries to git since last push did not work
Adding Apache libraries to git since last push two pushes did not work; just added library files to version control; hopefully that will commit these libraries
Updated SproutDailySummary data types to use Date and ints instead of just Strings; also made changes to GetSproutData.java to convert tokens to the appropriate types.
Added TicketMaster.java for TicketMaster data; also added GetTicketMasterData.java for processing TicketMaster .xls files.
Using ss.usermodel instead of hssf.usermodel to read both xls and xlsx files, not just xls files.

Update use of ss.usermodel; changed code not to skip a number of header lines but to count data collected in a line to know if it needs to process it; also updated file parse to be basicsummary file instead of myupcomingevents (and then updated ticketmaster data to reflect new fields); broke up the current reading function to make sheet reading function a separate helper function in anticipation of having to read more excel sheets and wanting to avoid duplicate code.

Took out the helper function for reading excel files; added TicketMasterTraffic.java for storing ticketmaster event details page (edp) traffic data; added new function to read in that edp traffic data file.

Added TicketMasterPriceLevels.java for storing event price levels breakdown; added new function to read in that pricing level data; also updated ticketmasterevents object to reflect updates in db schema; and tested more files with new updates.

Added GetIBDBData.java, GetNuviData.java, GetNuviTrendsHashtags.java, GetNuviTrendsKeywords.java, GetNuviTrendsNegativeTerms.java, GetNuviTrendsPositiveTerms.java, IBDBWeeklyGrosses.java, NuviDailySummary.java for processing nuvi and ibdb data; also updated GetSproutData to return a list
